- Excuse me, gentlemen.
- Starling.

1239
01:51:39,903 --> 01:51:42,363
Pitch, could you take our picture?

1240
01:51:42,906 --> 01:51:43,990
Sure.

1241
01:51:45,491 --> 01:51:48,328
Look, I just wanted to say congratulations.

1242
01:51:48,703 --> 01:51:50,580
And I'm not much good
at this kind of thing,

1243
01:51:50,663 --> 01:51:52,457
so I'm gonna duck out of here.

1244
01:51:52,540 --> 01:51:53,833
Okay, sure.

1245
01:51:55,543 --> 01:51:57,462
Thank you, Mr. Crawford.

1246
01:52:05,094 --> 01:52:07,847
Your father would have been proud today.

1247
01:52:10,767 --> 01:52:12,977
Don't forget your phone call.

1248
01:52:17,190 --> 01:52:18,483
Starling.

1249
01:52:18,691 --> 01:52:23,029
Well, Clarice,
have the lambs stopped screaming?

1250
01:52:23,696 --> 01:52:24,864
Dr. Lecter.

1251
01:52:25,114 --> 01:52:28,034
Don't bother with a trace.
I won't be on long enough.

1252
01:52:31,704 --> 01:52:35,917
- Where are you, Dr. Lecter?
- I have no plans to call on you, Clarice.

1253
01:52:36,000 --> 01:52:38,503
The world's more interesting
with you in it.

1254
01:52:39,045 --> 01:52:42,173
<i>So you take care now
to extend me the same courtesy.</i>

1255
01:52:42,256 --> 01:52:44,717
You know I can't make that promise.

1256
01:52:45,259 --> 01:52:47,929
I do wish we could chat longer, but...

1257
01:52:48,972 --> 01:52:51,557
I'm having an old friend for dinner.

1258
01:52:53,101 --> 01:52:54,185
Bye.

1259
01:52:54,811 --> 01:52:56,229
<i>Dr. Lecter...</i>

1260
01:52:58,690 --> 01:53:00,066
Dr. Lecter.

1261
01:53:02,360 --> 01:53:03,736
Dr. Lecter.

1262
01:53:05,738 --> 01:53:07,073
Dr. Lecter.

1263
01:53:07,615 --> 01:53:09,742
Hey, what? Oh, excuse me. I'm sorry.

1264
01:53:10,076 --> 01:53:12,996
- Is the security system all set up?
- We have the big-shot security.

1265
01:53:13,079 --> 01:53:14,580
Thank you. I appreciate that.
